ol.li:
Substitute x = 9 into the expression to find
            \begin{align*}
                2x + \sqrt[3]{x - 1} \amp = 2(\alert{9}) + \sqrt[3]{\alert{9} - 1}\\
                                    \amp = 18 +  \sqrt[3]{8} = 20\\
             \end{align*}

